				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/cheats.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>

			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Unlock Billy Gunn -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Win King of the Ring during year onefont>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Cactus Jack -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play season mode until you get to the pay per view event No Way Out</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Deadman Undertaker parts in Create-A-Wrestler -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Find and beat the character known as "Unknown R" in Season Mode</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Debra -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At Raw after the Royal Rumble during year 1, Debra will be backstage. She will ask Vince to be in a beauty contest. After that she is unlocked</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Mean Street Posse -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">They will be shown backstage. After the event all three are unlocked</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Michael Cole -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play in season mode and get to the first week of April in year two</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Mick Foley -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play season mode until you get to Wrestlemania</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Shawn Michaels -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play season mode until you get to the May pay per view event Judgement Day</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Stone Cold -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Go to Backslash in the first year of season mode, then complete the event with Stone Cold</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock TLC Match -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play season mode until August of 2000 when a TLC match takes place</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Everything -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play season mode through until you get to Wrestlemania in year five, then win the match</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Wrestlemania 2000 Commercial -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Play in season mode and get to the fourth week of March</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Get 225 ability points -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When you can create five features for your wrestler, put the four weak body parts and ''The Iron King.'' You'll get 225 ability points for your character</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Hidden Backstage Areas - Shower room -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enter the locker room. Whip your opponent into the center of the wall directly across the weights/gym equipment. A hole should form, which leads to the shower room.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Hidden Backstage Areas - Boiler room -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Go to the basement. Go over to the door with the yellow banners over it. Whip your opponent into the grating directly to the right of the door. It should break, and form an opening, leading to the boiler room..</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Hidden Backstage Areas - WWF New York -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">In Season Mode, you should see a cut scene, with Michael Cole saying WWF New York will be opening in one month. After a few more shows, there will be another cut scene of Michael Cole in WWF New York. When you go down to the basement, you can now enter WWF New York.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>

     </tr>
</table>

